And although she was on a day off from her estimated £600,000-a-year job, her lustrous skin and carefully put together designer outfit – complete with chunky gold watch and pearl earrings – showed she wasn’t holding back in the style stakes.

But perhaps the excitement of such an unusual occasion was too much for the mother-of-three.

She was pictured pulling an array of astonishing expressions as she joined in a class promoting healthy eating with the Kirkintilloch school’s pupils and her husband Nick.  

